### 1960s: The Era of Rock and Pop Ascendancy

The 1960s were a pivotal decade for music festivals, marked by the explosion of [rock and pop music](/Rock_and_pop_music) and the rise of large-scale outdoor gatherings. These events became crucibles for burgeoning genres and countercultural movements.

